<p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://www.futilitycloset.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/2025-12-04-same-thing.jpg" alt="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:October_sky_poster.jpg" width="260" height="389" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-72228" /></p>
<p>In 1998, as aerospace engineer Homer Hickam&#8217;s memoir <em>Rocket Boys</em> was being adapted for the screen, Universal Studios&#8217; research warned that women over 30 would not see a movie with that title.</p>
<p>So the name was changed to <em>October Sky</em> &#8212; the same 10 letters in a different order.</p>
